@startuml Auth_Module\nTitle Auth Module - Controllers, Services, Guards\nleft to right direction\nskinparam componentStyle rectangle\n\npackage "Auth" {\n  [AuthController] as AuthController\n  [AuthService] as AuthService\n  [JwtStrategy] as JwtStrategy\n}\n\npackage "Shared" {\n  [PrismaModule] as Prisma\n  [JwtAuthGuard] as JwtAuthGuard\n}\n\nAuthController --> AuthService : login/register/refresh\nAuthService --> Prisma : users, tokens\nJwtStrategy ..> Prisma : validate user\nAuthController ..> JwtAuthGuard : protected routes\n\n@enduml